Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.50,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本字幕由澄空学园制作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架空武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了更精确  效率地进行物质变换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(276,323)\fs18}Dark  matter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将上位元素构架成武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅的  缇娅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙  龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是龙哟  是龙哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这些并不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  将所有的虚伪抛去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做回真正的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,40)\pos(578,72)\blur3}祸焰的穆斯贝尔海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,40)\pos(578,72)\bord0\shad1.5}祸焰的穆斯贝尔海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…你在摸哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只龙是缇娅对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  恐怕是架空武装化成了龙的形态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅现在  已经完全认为自己是龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话必须要让她恢复正常才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Gungnir
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿吧  闪光！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿吧  闪光！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅  缇娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果造成的伤害再大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来之后必须要跟她说才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是立川穗乃花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教  物部悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是学校中唯一的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  你受伤了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在物质变换的练习中失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了点轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我个忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请轻一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立川你也是从巴西利斯克移动方向的小镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被带回来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在那种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为母亲会在世界各地到处来去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也和母亲一起到处漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样被分开  你不会感到寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我们之间也并不算亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没有父亲或者其他亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为无可奈何所以才在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  不如说正因能够自立而松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  没有人陪着你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有跟班上的人混熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么困难  随时可以来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请多指教了  立川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我穗乃花就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能直接叫你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么悠  告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  物部少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事我有点在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算也告诉你一声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的信奉者团体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始实行缇娅·莱特宁格的夺回行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米德加尔的防护很牢固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要入侵并没有这么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  那家伙就一定会出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙？难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  与尼福尔敌对的「D」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽·史尔特·穆斯贝尔海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是那个奇丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会做出什么行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计那个时候会造成巨大的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后会给你发最新的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有万一  就期待你的表现咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记住了  洛基少校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么缇娅会睡着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎呢  大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要和你谈一些重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说缇娅现在你觉得比昨天更喜欢大家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  丽莎和大家都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  刚才缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一些就让丽莎受伤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了狂暴的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演习场也被破坏的乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…缇娅  那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要好好地向大家道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再把自己想做成龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  缇娅是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅是可爱的人类女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  缇娅是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我有着这样的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还有我  都拥有着同样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们以人类的身份生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果缇娅要以龙的身份活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没办法在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望缇娅能选择以人类的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅的爸爸妈妈在哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  都被烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅见到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:11:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！  全部都烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是家  还是那些人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的  所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我这些  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  哥哥  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都非常担心你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅  给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指刚才的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有人在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也没在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就给你些惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对渴求赎罪的人就应当给予惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不在你被罪恶感所击溃之前了结这一切的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子缇娅就把过错都弥补了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不用烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛了  谢谢你  丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  明天的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去玩怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部  缇娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？这可是我新买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  之前的那件被海浪冲走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的事不要去想了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然伊莉丝很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什什什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都这样说了…  我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  那缇娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  缇娅很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是可爱怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  伊莉丝是缇娅的竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和缇娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！我一定不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把棍子的弄倒那方就算输了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！我接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻  让你见识下我的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅  再来一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要让你见识下我的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论来几次都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我并不愿意让你看到我的泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是勉为其难地穿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我总觉得是精心挑选出来的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得弄防晒什么的太麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怎么会到海里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对着不太习惯一时间有些迷茫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我觉得很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…那当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不用你说我也清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  刚才的话差不多就算是性骚扰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在抒发感想而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随随便便对女性的泳装发表评价
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便被说是性骚扰也无可厚非吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那关于深月的  我还是什么都不说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我并不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥的话而会觉得害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常适合你  背部还挺性感的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你说让我随便说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅又赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一遍好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一遍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里也看书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看书很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是难得来了海边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放开一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们来玩玩沙滩排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是唯独哥哥只要失手一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须接受惩罚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让男生只有你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的条件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  钓不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今晚的第一颗星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？这可是我的倾力之作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  好累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  你真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇娅真的会游泳了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  再教教缇娅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强可不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你在做一些十分过瘾的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道园长也想埋在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要和穿着泳装的清纯少女们卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉你的形容让我感觉到时代的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  我踩你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经在踩了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会两手空空就来加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经准备好礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着秀色可餐的清纯少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再饮下这一口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是太爽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您来这里不会只是来看泳衣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  来看她也是一个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定会选择作为人类的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是真正的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是按人类的方式生存的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能成为人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活方式比容颜姿态更为宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  盛宴才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去和清纯的少女们卿卿我我喽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱吧  舞动吧  少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多留一下也无妨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  玛伊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啊  你帮我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我还没有和她们…卿…卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有关奇丽的最新资料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇丽·史尔特·穆斯贝尔海姆  性别女」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「身高约160厘米  年龄不明  国籍不详」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约在3年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便作为龙信奉者团体的首领开始活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认为与她有关的恐怖事件超过300件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便不直接触碰也能让人或者物品燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个善于生成火焰的「D」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  选择了作为龙的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让缇娅变成这家伙一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永青之赫卡同克瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一点招呼都不打就出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过向龙询问这些想来也是没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对不会把缇娅交给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是我们重要的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:23:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在红红燃烧的火焰当中…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  枪皇无尽的法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Tiamat
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红翼龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物部悠  让我见识下你作为男子的气概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}選ばれた運命を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:15.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}生き抜くたび　隣にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:32.00,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ひとりで立ち向かった　あの戦いで分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:36.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}多分、全てなんて変えられやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:44.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}頼りない武装でも　君を救って行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:54.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}思い出せないほどに　時が経つまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:56.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Far  away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Find  the  way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly  Fafnir
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:02.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}才能も超えて上昇する！
